column2: SELECT   p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,   p.deVAB_g,p.deVAB_i, p.deVAB_r, p.deVAB_u, p.deVAB_z,   p.deVABErr_g, p.deVABErr_i, p.deVABErr_r, p.deVABErr_u, p.deVABErr_z,   s.plate,s.mjd,s.fiberID into mydb.MyTable from PhotoObj AS p   JOIN SpecObjAll s ON p.objid = s.BestObjid   JOIN MyDB.Best_Medium as b ON b.Plate = s.plate and b.MJD = s.mjd and b.Fiber = s.fiberID
